{"tid":485063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[貴族遊戲]因為係名校權貴出身所以先咁多人討論","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T16:07:56.000Z","uid":77936,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"877ede6b3a2c4e3c924b2d3fff934046c3a55753","tid":485063,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"何苦要參一腳入去佢地嘅貴族遊戲 俾人撚狗咁撚 <br />\n成件事由發布到放大 一個鐘都唔洗就知成件事都係曬人地預訂計劃之內<br />\n連培正都提到三星期前已經知道 教練只不過係得罪權貴的犧牲品<br />\n真相根本不重要 因為教練已經被人格謀殺<br />\n再多的輿論都無用 因為名校權貴有特權<br />\n<br />\n由見到咩信耶撚 做過義工 咩委員會幹事 港大 名校出身 犯刑事最後都係社會服務令 <br />\n對比同件刑事 窮人中產都要含撚執番鹼<br />\n<br />\n呢個社會再理性都已經維持唔到公義"},{"pid":"10b406ecaae3bcd157a6ca3f095c89205b18f566","tid":485063,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n人就係生而不平等"},{"pid":"3be69f764d523b8737ec72981b341651f1ed4a30","tid":485063,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，最新確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n<d